// 回归：expr 宏展开成块表达式后，@async_fn 中的局部绑定与 pre-await 求值
// 不能在 poll/resume 间丢失或重复执行。

use std.async;
use std.testing.assert_eq_i32;

var g_macro_preawait_eval_count: i32 = 0;

fn seed_once(v: i32) i32 {
    g_macro_preawait_eval_count = g_macro_preawait_eval_count + 1;
    return v;
}

struct PendingOnce : Future<!i32> {
    stage: i32,

    fn poll(self: &Self, waker: &Waker) Poll<!i32> {
        _ = waker;
        if self.stage == 0 {
            self.stage = 1;
            return Poll<!i32>.Pending({});
        }
        return Poll<!i32>.Ready(ok<i32>(2));
    }

    fn release(self: &Self) void {
        _ = self;
    }
}

fn pending_once() Future<!i32> {
    return PendingOnce{ stage: 0 };
}

mc add_with_local(base: expr) expr {
    @mc_code(@mc_ast({
        const seeded: i32 = seed_once(${base});
        seeded + 1;
    }));
}

@async_fn
fn async_macro_block_expr() Future<!i32> {
    const sum: i32 = add_with_local(39);
    const delta: i32 = try @await pending_once();
    return sum + delta;
}

test "async_expr_macro_block_keeps_preawait_eval_once" {
    g_macro_preawait_eval_count = 0;

    const w: Waker = Waker{};
    const f: Future<!i32> = async_macro_block_expr();

    const p1: Poll<!i32> = f.poll(&w);
    var pending_seen: i32 = 0;
    match p1 {
        .Pending(_) => { pending_seen = 1; },
        .Ready(_) => { pending_seen = 0; },
    };
    try assert_eq_i32(pending_seen, 1);
    try assert_eq_i32(g_macro_preawait_eval_count, 1);

    const p2: Poll<!i32> = f.poll(&w);
    var result: i32 = -1;
    match p2 {
        .Pending(_) => { result = -2; },
        .Ready(r) => { result = r catch { -3; }; },
    };
    try assert_eq_i32(result, 42);
    try assert_eq_i32(g_macro_preawait_eval_count, 1);
}
